(Outlook Email Sync Issue) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Keywords: outlook email not syncing email not loading mail stuck email error) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Steps to fix Outlook not syncing emails:) Tj T*
(1. Restart Outlook completely \(close from taskbar too\).) Tj T*
(2. Check your internet connection.) Tj T*
(3. Go to File then Account Settings and verify your account.) Tj T*
(4. Click Send and Receive All Folders \(F9 shortcut\).) Tj T*
(5. Clear Outlook cache: close Outlook, delete the OST file, reopen.) Tj T*
(6. Run Outlook in safe mode: press Win+R, type outlook.exe /safe) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Advanced Fix:) Tj T*
(- Remove and re-add your email account in Account Settings.) Tj T*
(- Repair Office: Control Panel > Programs > Microsoft Office > Repair.) Tj T*
(- Check mailbox storage quota is not full.) Tj T*
(- Contact IT if issue persists after all above steps.) Tj T*
ET

